ttsburgh/", "1/united states/ohio/", "2/united states/ohio/mahoning/", "3/united states/ohio/mahoning/youngstown/"], "contributor": ["ohio history connection, columbus, oh"], "date": "1958-02-19", "dates": ["1958-02-19"], "description": ["fage S THAT WE ty aay to SUPREME edit rerie or rtjMl ANOTHER And now forward i Kapa vam dolje This ZAJEDNI\u010cAR 1 77lis HAAustralianc v i Life Story P 11 Steve Lipanovich Secy Horsing Mf Around To Burn Americas teevee net Irish CroatiaMationai Home Offices CROATIAN FRATERNAL I N ION Pittsburgh Pennsylvania THE Croatian Fraternal Union is much more than merely interested in the American Croatian Singers Federation ACSF should come as no surprise Comprised of choirs affiliated with its two component Alliances Faller and Mihanovicthe ACSF came into being in Gary Ind May 30 1949 with the formal adoption of bylaws and the election of leaders to govern the at long last amalgamated cultural groups It was on that historic oc casion that the Croatian Fra ternal Union first donated 50000 to the fledgling Federation and pledged it its moral and material support That promise has been kept inviolate to this date The Croatian Fraternal Union again showed its faith in the future of the ACSF when the Delegates to the Societys 9th Natl Quadrennial Convention of 1955 voted the Federation another grant this time the amount of 100000 Could the ACSF continue to exist with out the"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-09-04T23:18:31.585Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84024547/1958-02-19/ed-1/?sp=8", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_frederick_ver02:data:sn84024547:00279555776:1958021901:0096/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=260&w=198", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_frederick_ver02:data:sn84024547:00279555776:1958021901:0096/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=521&w=397", "h